Author: emelinette
Text: 24 and I’ve been feeling the exact same! Something about reading the posts on here makes everything feel a little less impossible. It can seem *so* endless... thinking of you and hoping you have more of the good days and fewer darker ones - please feel free to message me about anything at all ❤️☺️
